vestment management.", "bbox": [153.2, 1316.0, 563.3, 1336.9]}, {"text": "During fiscal 2008, the Company’s investment committee made the decision to change the target", "bbox": [194.9, 1353.5, 1077.4, 1374.4]}, {"text": "asset allocation of the U.S. plans’ master trust from 60% equity and 40% fixed income to 30% equity", "bbox": [153.2, 1378.5, 1081.3, 1399.4]}, {"text": "108", "bbox": [153.2, 1475.5, 184.5, 1496.3]}]}